description: Demolition of all existing buildings on site and the erection of 3 buildings providing a total of 60 residential units (Use Class C3) (100% affordable housing) and 524 sqm of flexible commercial floorspace (Use Classes, A1, A2,  A3, A4, A5, B1 and/or D1); to be provided within one 4 storey building (block A) with commercial units on the ground floor and residential flats on the upper floors, two part 3/ part 2 storey buildings (Block B/Terrace A and Terrace B) serving residential accommodation with the provision of 7 parking spaces (incorporating 6 disabled spaces and 1 car club space), associated means of access, cycle parking, refuse stores, associated landscaping and amenity space.
